        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "It is very, _very_ unlikely that we will ban AI assisted contributions (as some of the core maintainers see this -- reasonably so -- as a very useful tool that improve their ability to contribute). There will very likely be an AI policy  in the near future, which at the very least will require (detailed) disclosure and prohibit direct agent contributions (\"vibe coding\"), and possibly prohibit LLM comments and PR descriptions as well.",
