        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I felt I need to write this here. I can think of several different cases where one may consider their own contribution as \"AI assisted\":\n- Generating an entire solution to the problem using AI, and not making any further modifications.\n- Generating a solution to the problem using AI, and then making some of their own modifications.\n- Writing a solution on their own, and then adjusting the code based on AI suggestions.\n- Writing a solution on their own, and then using AI to generate tests.\n- Using AI to analyze the problem, and then writing a solution based on the analysis.\n- Using AI to verify their own analysis or solution.",
            "created_at": "2026-03-09T23:09:54Z",
